## Remarks

<span data-ttu-id="2d705-1193">可以用如下代码来循环访问内存范围内的块：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d705-1193">You can iterate the chunks in the memory range with code like the following:</span></span>

```csharp
foreach (ReadOnlyMemory<char> chunk in sb.GetChunks())
    foreach(char ch in chunk.Span)
        { /* operations on ch */ }
```

<span data-ttu-id="2d705-1194">此方法的目的是有效地提取*常量*<xref:System.Text.StringBuilder>的数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d705-1194">The purpose of this method is to efficiently extract the data of a *constant* <xref:System.Text.StringBuilder>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2d705-1195">如果在块区枚举不完整时修改了 <xref:System.Text.StringBuilder>，则结果是不确定的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d705-1195">If the <xref:System.Text.StringBuilder> is modified while the chunk enumeration is incomplete, the result is undefined.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2d705-1196"><xref:System.Text.StringBuilder> 也不是线程安全的，因此在并发线程上对其进行操作是非法的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d705-1196"><xref:System.Text.StringBuilder> is also not thread-safe, so operating on it with concurrent threads is illegal.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2d705-1197">如果修改了 <xref:System.Text.StringBuilder>，则返回的 <xref:System.ReadOnlyMemory%601> 块不会保持不变，因此，不会将它们缓存供以后使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d705-1197">The <xref:System.ReadOnlyMemory%601> chunks returned are not guaranteed to remain unchanged if the <xref:System.Text.StringBuilder> is modified, so do not cache them for later use.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="2d705-1198">使用 <xref:System.ReadOnlyMemory%601> 创建 <xref:System.ReadOnlySpan%601> （与在上一个示例中的 <xref:System.ReadOnlyMemory%601.Span?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法非常昂贵，因此，如果需要在嵌套的 `for` 语句中使用它，请为范围创建一个本地变量。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d705-1198">Creating a <xref:System.ReadOnlySpan%601> from a <xref:System.ReadOnlyMemory%601> (as the <xref:System.ReadOnlyMemory%601.Span?displayProperty=nameWithType> method does in the previous example, is expensive, so create a local variable for the span if you need to use it in a nested `for` statement.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2d705-1199">例如：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2d705-1199">For example:</span></span>

```csharp
foreach (ReadOnlyMemory<char> chunk in sb.GetChunks())
{
    var span = chunk.Span;
    for(int i = 0; i < span.Length; i++)
    {
        /* operations on span[i] */
    }
}
```
